Demo for generating flow from a Linux host and displaying it in New Relic.

1) Create a free account at https://newrelic.com/.

2) Follow the guided install for "Network Flow". Copy the account ID and API Key generated.

3) Run with

sudo NETWORK=$MY_NETWORK NR_LICENSE_KEY=$MY_KEY NR_ACCOUNT_ID=$MY_ACCOUNT_ID docker-compose up

For example,

sudo NETWORK='^eth' NR_LICENSE_KEY=foobarrrraaaaNRAL NR_ACCOUNT_ID=3222432 docker-compose up

Want more? We also offer support for containers and kubernetes networking with:

* https://kentiklabs.com/blog/container-visibility/
* https://kentiklabs.com/blog/visualize-k8s-traffic/